  "title": "(Electrical) Sales Executive |Up to $4.4k basic + $800 yearly allowances + VB | West - LQ",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location: </strong>Pioneer <br /><strong>Working Hours: </strong>Mon – Fri, office hour<br /><br /><strong>Salary Package:</strong></p><ul><li>Basic up to $4,400 (depending on experience)</li><li>OT Payable </li><li>Variable Bonus (Mid-Year & Year-End)</li><li>$800 allowances annually</li></ul><p><strong>Key Duties:</strong></p><ul><li>Manage sales enquiries and promote electrical products to new and existing customers.</li><li>Identify and develop new business opportunities through calls, emails, and networking.</li><li>Prepare quotations, proposals, and pricing; handle sales negotiations.</li><li>Conduct presentations, prepare market analyses, and compile sales forecasts/reports.</li><li>Build and maintain strong client relationships with ongoing support.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Electrical/Electronics Engineering or related field </li><li>At least 1 year of sales or customer service experience in industrial components or related field preferred.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office and CRM systems.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Apply now and be part of a growing and reputable team in the technician industry!</p><p>Please submit your updated resume on Whatsapp at wa.me/6587504643 or press the APPLY NOW BUTTON.</p><p>By submitting your resume and/or personal information, you consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of your personal data by the company (or its designated agent) for the purposes of processing, administration and managing your job application.</p><p>Please be notified that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><br /></p><p>Charlotte Loh| Reg No.: R25127073</p><p>Griffin HR Consultancy Pte Ltd | EA Licence No.: 23C1449</p>",
